quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  96,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  96,1,( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) apne perwar-digaar ka naam le kar parho jis ne ( aalam ko ) pedakiya
  96,2,jis ne ensaan ko khoon ki phatki se banaya
  96,3,parho aur tumhara perwar-digaar bara kareem hai
  96,4,jis ne qalam ke zariye se ilm sikhaya
  96,5,aur ensaan ko woh baatein skhayin jis ka is ko ilm nah tha
  96,6,magar ensaan sarkash ho jata hai
  96,7,jab ke apne tiyn ghanni daikhta hai
  96,8,kuch shak nahi ke ( is ko ) tumahray perwar-digaar hi ki taraf lout kar jana hai
  96,9,bhala tum ne is shakhs ko dekha jo mana karta hai
  96,10,( yani ) aik bande ko jab woh namaz parhnay lagta hai
  96,11,bhala dekho to agar yeh raah e raast par ho
  96,12,ya parhaiz gari ka hukum kere ( to mana karna kaisa )
  96,13,aur dekho to agar is ne deen haq ko jhatlaya aur is se munh morra ( tokiya howa )
  96,14,kiyaas ko maloom nahi ke khuda dekh raha hai
  96,15,dekho agar woh baz nah aeye ga to hum ( is ki ) peshani ke baal pakar ghasetein ge
  96,16,yani is jhutay khatakaar ki peshani ke baal
  96,17,to woh apne yaaron ki majlis ko bula lay
  96,18,hum bhi apne moklan dozakh ko bulaa len ge
  96,19,dekho is ka kaha nah maanna aur qrbِ ( khuda ) haasil karte rehna
